Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE LAST ATTACK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Seems pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Making up for lost Aura with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, your Raiden Strash...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is far weaker than\Nthat new attack of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why sheath your sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! He has that new scabbard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This scabbard is a new weapon\Nmade by Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My sword can't get any stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But with this scabbard, I can increase\Nthe power of my Magic Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I sheath my Magic Sword like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the Magic Power is amplified inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When I draw it again, the spell will have\Nbecome its strongest iteration!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So his Raiden will become a Gigaden spell?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Rura spell?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he move over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magic Power amplification takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He did that to buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai is confident that his next attack\Nis going to be insanely strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He distanced himself so that\Nwe wouldn't get hurt by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, I won't try to stop you anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe in that power of yours\Nthat's made miracle after miracle happen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give him everything you've got!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he can use Gigaden,\Nthere's only one attack he'll use.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The last gift from\Nhis dead father, Gigabrake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could stop him right now, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this attack will kill me anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall use these few seconds\Nto increase my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}GIGABRAKE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Then I shall match it\Nwith my greatest, final attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Using all of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Ultra Combustion Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}ULTRA COMBUSTION SLASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now witness this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shatter before this single strike\Nthat contains my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't shatter this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what every battle has led to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest attack I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}GIGA STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Giga Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Giga Strash...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He really won! Dai did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it for Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a Superior Being,\Nnow that Hadorra has been defeated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he's going crumble to black ash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Albinass... I understand now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}why you were willing to\Ngive your life to prevent this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always lost to Aban and his students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban's attack with Baran's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that another attack\Nyou created in your training?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I came up with it just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt I needed the power I got\Nfrom both Master and Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I couldn't defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tried it at the last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So in all of that you created\Nthe most powerful attack ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\NI thought I could defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Being at my lowest when I couldn't\Ndefeat you was when my life really began.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was short,\Nbut it was indeed fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Dai, the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For my last wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,at least let me touch the hand\Nthat defeated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,before my body crumbles to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A flute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoyed that, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That melody was a little elegy from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To the two who gave everything\Nto show us a magnificent fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too weakened to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth, flames of the Underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Isn't my Kill Trap splendid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kill Trap"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Trap of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban Palace is full of\Nvarious traps that I've laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nine of Diamonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It lets me summon the most powerful\Nflames of the Underworld at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate spellcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I could have activated it\Nthe moment you entered Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for Dai and Hadorra\Nto be exhausted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You dare defile an honorable duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!\NForget about Kilban right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We have to help Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's futile, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it's already too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The eight all-consuming flames\Ngather at the central point{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and all living creatures within\Nare incinerated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No power can ever escape it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets to die with the Hero,\Nso Hadorra should be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assume it'll work out that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured something like this\Nwould happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as I'm here,\Ndon't expect your schemes to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGA STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ULTRA COMBUSTION SLASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as I'm here,\Ndon't expect your schemes to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Dai's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You dove in just before the trap closed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that Ban would try something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra and his Royal Guard\Nmay be honorable,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is Ban Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is as untrustworthy as\Na fair fight from the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always that brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kilban disappeared?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why would he after his trap was thwarted?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! My Hyadaruko spell\Ncan't hold it off forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody hurry up and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!\NMy Hyadaruko spell isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Popp's is holding it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp's Magic Power is\Nmuch stronger than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there...\NIsn't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, they'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using Grand Cross?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This trap can't be broken by normal means!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be blown away\Nby the greatest power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of energy output,\Nno attack can beat Grand Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Hyunckel's going to use Grand Cross!\NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Popp!\NExpect this to hurt a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Grand Cross!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it repel my Grand Cross?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nothing's happened in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It had no effect on the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...\Nthe reason the Reaper retreated...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see what lovely faces\Nthe humans make?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can't match you\Nin terms of cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the cruelest\Nin the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?! What can we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, we can't just stand by\Nand watch them get burned to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess knows that!\NThat's why she remains silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the greatest Aura energy\Nof Grand Cross was repelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that trap can only be broken\Nby magical means.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it wouldn't explain\Nwhy Grand Cross had no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp is holding off the flames\Ninside with his Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But, out here, none of us\Nhave Magic Power even close to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That means there's only one way\Nfor us to rescue those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to defeat Kilban,\Nthe one using the spellcraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that all to well,\Nwhich is why he retreated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To somewhere deep in Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding and defeating him now\Nwill take too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's closed off\Nour only hope of saving them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right.\NLeona and I don't have the Magic Power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona! Use Minakator!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in the Cave of Trials, even\Nincomplete, casting Minakator should...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good... Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to stop Ban Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I already used Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is already being affected\Nby my Minakator spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Purification Spells have no effect\Nif the same person casts them twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a waste of Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How... How can you be so calm, Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we have to remain collected\Nat times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to focus\Nand figure out what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our enemy is far beyond us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the minds of evil geniuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Leona.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good, Maam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Physical power will never work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your firsts or my Wave Strike\Nhad any effect on those flames,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kilban would never have left\Nwithout taking us out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, Popp! Don't give up in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They do love their futile resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Popp are caught\Nin Kilban's trap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The blazing flames of the Underworld\Nclose in on them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As their stamina ebbs and all seems lost,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a single ray of light shines down on Popp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Dai and Popp escape\Nfrom Kilban's Kill Trap?{\i0}
